Class Summary
BiotecSplashScreen SplashScreen for OboEdit

DataExtraction Abstract class for different FileTyps, which will be read out.

Author:
(Atif Iqbal), Thomas Waechter The Ontology Generation package. The Ontology Generation Plugin gives support for automatic terminology recognition, definition extraction and placing new defined terms in the ontology structure.
